{"tid":166800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟香港有乜好？","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T12:08:02.000Z","uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c62c25eb000cd22047b462cf89f8b21747a6e6","tid":166800,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"人口密度高到仆街<br />\n<br />\n出街 番工 放工 日日好似養豬場咁逼<br />\n<br />\n連以前行山係想遠離人群 而家大東山都變旺角<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓價升到仆街<br />\n<br />\n無父幹既 就算大學生都係畢業打份萬零蚊工<br />\n<br />\n要養自己養屋企 三十歲都供唔起樓 婚後都要同父母同住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gy4HYp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGy4HYp8.jpg&h=d4854ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓價越黎越高 細用面積越黎越細 但發展商仲可以繼續賣花讚花香<br />\n<br />\n就算買到樓 你求神拜佛唔好俾人炒 一炒係咁先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政治上 指鹿為馬 黑白不非 利益永遠行先<br />\n<br />\n社會上又多問題 又要俾少數族裔洽 俾人打都唔識還手<br />\n<br />\n同大富翁一樣 各行各業插晒旗 發達機會又少左<br />\n<br />\n民怨越積越深 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟有乜好？"},{"pid":"d4ed1098c42d9f711773503ab677be46cb24fb9f","tid":166800,"uid":33326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"a85b804c0892790b7ec1e6426d8a288d85e4363f","tid":166800,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得咁多人走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dd308341090ef9cd9d979c3f6e9ed02d5b74ac","tid":166800,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:08:02.000Z","msg":"一無是處，但係我愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}